quran[7]{c,v,t}:
  54,1,"The Hour has drawn near and the moon has ruptured."
  54,2,"Yet whenever they see a miracle, they disregard(it) and say, “Continuous magic!”"
  54,3,"And they disbelieved and followed their whims. And every <span class=""h"">matter is bound to settle</span>[1666]",footnotes:1:<span class="qiraat-footnote">Qira’at: Abu Ja’far read it as: “And every settled matter (has drawn near).”</span>
  54,4,"And most surely there have come to them tidings containing a deterrent—"
  54,5,"profound wisdom, but warnings are of no avail."
  54,6,"So turn awaysg from them. On the day when the Summoner summons to something terrible,"